      "title": "JoSAA 2026 — Complete Engineering Aptitude Assessment",
      "bodyText": "English\nதமிழ்\nSheets: Connected\nJOSAA 2026\nComplete Engineering Aptitude Assessment\n\nA scientific, multi-dimensional assessment to discover your ideal engineering branch\n\n1\nProfile\n2\nRIASEC\n3\nSkills\n4\nSWOT\n5\nBranches\n6\nVision\n7\nParents\n8\nAnalysis\n9\nReport\n📝 Student Profile\nLet's start with some basic information about you.\nFull Name / பெயர்\nEmail / மின்னஞ்சல்\nPhone / தொலைபேசி\nSchool Name / பள்ளி பெயர்\n+2 / 12th Board / 12ஆம் வகுப்பு போர்டு\nSelect\nCBSE\nICSE\nState Board\n12th Percentage / Score / 12ஆம் வகுப்பு மதிப்பெண்\nJEE Main Expected/Actual Rank / JEE Main தரவரிசை\nJEE Advanced Rank (if applicable) / JEE Advanced தரவரிசை\nCategory / பிரிவு\nSelect\nGeneral\nOBC-NCL\nSC\nST\nEWS\nPwD\nHome State / சொந்த மாநிலம்\nSelect\nAndhra Pradesh\nAssam\nBihar\nChhattisgarh\nDelhi\nGoa\nGujarat\nHaryana\nHimachal Pradesh\nJammu & Kashmir\nJharkhand\nKarnataka\nKerala\nMadhya Pradesh\nMaharashtra\nManipur\nMeghalaya\nMizoram\nNagaland\nOdisha\nPunjab\nRajasthan\nSikkim\nTamil Nadu\nTelangana\nTripura\nUttar Pradesh\nUttarakhand\nWest Bengal\nNext →",
